{"tid":1924812,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"油價大跌，入油費不變","createTime":"2020-03-14T02:16:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-14T11:51:02.000Z","uid":90304,"like":31,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"462f866ac985ea15e7a5be1f0e284ed71bfd59a6","tid":1924812,"uid":90304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T02:16:21.000Z","msg":"高油價是政府政策，目的是減少汽車數目。(油價大跌, 入油費不變, 油商繼續合謀定價)<br />\n<br />\n減少教車師傅發牌，目的是減少汽車數目。(垃圾教車師傅生CANCER快D死, 教得唔好收得又貴)<br />\n<br />\n減少考牌官數量，目的是減少汽車數目。(考車肥一次唔知要排幾耐呢? )<br />\n<br />\n減少泊車車位，目的是減少汽車數目。(繼續炒車位fat fat, 收租佬萬歲)<br />\n<br />\n私家車首次登記稅偏高，目的是減少汽車數目。(政府 fat fat, 唔使做有稅收)<br />\n<br />\n全港有多條行車天橋淪為「斷橋」，閒置20多年無人問津，料浪費數以億計港元公帑。目的是政府唔想做野，唔想幫星斗市民紓緩路面狀況，有錢你同我去排西隧快靚正。<br />\n<br />\n香港政府，以不變，應萬變。"},{"pid":"c77427babf594faa7df0632ac0d19209a0dc105e","tid":1924812,"uid":35699,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T02:17:44.000Z","msg":"有跌過嘅油價"},{"pid":"7f999ccb73b4007c1344aa4976b8cba3154d9591","tid":1924812,"uid":90304,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"c77427babf594faa7df0632ac0d19209a0dc105e","tid":1924812,"uid":35699,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T02:17:44.000Z","msg":"有跌過嘅油價"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T02:19:16.000Z","msg":"易升難跌"},{"pid":"0b2e2e3f76e3d4a0db51255984d1697e2b73fe2a","tid":1924812,"uid":90304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T02:19:41.000Z","msg":"電子道路收費都係講多過做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c3d9425548de3b84cb6161b9b5844523b547f55","tid":1924812,"uid":90304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T02:20:31.000Z","msg":"有無車主入黎分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da026ed6ad80250c350b86e4765e79ea0547b3d4","tid":1924812,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T02:21:20.000Z","msg":"唔係"},{"pid":"c5ea9ffba4eaade994e9060d916e5b72df491604","tid":1924812,"uid":186882,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T02:21:22.000Z","msg":"世界油平啫<br />\n中海油唔平嘛"},{"pid":"e6f16e0ae5815f4cebc60f024413545fa9d0ab5c","tid":1924812,"uid":275225,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T02:22:35.000Z","msg":"已經入到麻木咗<br />\n唔知幾錢一L...<br />\n淨係知貴過澳洲一倍"},{"pid":"ddbab3aea210281f053530cc327af7da5c806279","tid":1924812,"uid":90304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T02:27:48.000Z","msg":"油公司給予大車隊的折扣高達50%，但小車主最多也只是20%，當中的差異除了突顯折扣優惠不透明及不公平外，還可以看到燃油價格的確存在相當大的減價空間。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%91%A8%E5%A0%B1/277181/%E7%AB%B6%E7%88%AD%E6%B3%95-%E6%B2%B9%E5%83%B9%E7%A9%A9%E5%A6%82%E6%B3%B0%E5%B1%B1-%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E5%A0%B1%E5%91%8A%E7%99%BC%E8%A1%A8%E4%B8%80%E5%B9%B4%E7%87%83%E6%B2%B9%E5%83%B9%E6%A0%BC%E6%9C%AA%E8%A6%8B%E5%9B%9E%E8%90%BD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%2591%25A8%25E5%25A0%25B1%2F277181%2F%25E7%25AB%25B6%25E7%2588%25AD%25E6%25B3%2595-%25E6%25B2%25B9%25E5%2583%25B9%25E7%25A9%25A9%25E5%25A6%2582%25E6%25B3%25B0%25E5%25B1%25B1-%25E7%25A0%2594%25E7%25A9%25B6%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E5%2591%258A%25E7%2599%25BC%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E7%2587%2583%25E6%25B2%25B9%25E5%2583%25B9%25E6%25A0%25BC%25E6%259C%25AA%25E8%25A6%258B%25E5%259B%259E%25E8%2590%25BD&d=B95HL5QQ1MLE%2FldfuzA7j67%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=2ba18221\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%91%A8%E5%A0%B1/277181/%E7%AB%B6%E7%88%AD%E6%B3%95-%E6%B2%B9%E5%83%B9%E7%A9%A9%E5%A6%82%E6%B3%B0%E5%B1%B1-%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E5%A0%B1%E5%91%8A%E7%99%BC%E8%A1%A8%E4%B8%80%E5%B9%B4%E7%87%83%E6%B2%B9%E5%83%B9%E6%A0%BC%E6%9C%AA%E8%A6%8B%E5%9B%9E%E8%90%BD</a>"},{"pid":"cb34df568bb0c123b7a924df9910865b9636fa37","tid":1924812,"uid":90304,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T02:38:28.000Z","msg":"市場高度集中於數個燃油零售商，由煉油、進口至油站銷售，「一條龍」式供應燃油（中國石油除外）。<br />\n<br />\n進入市場的門檻高；新經營者要有足夠油站及碼頭倉庫設施，尤其困難。<br />\n<br />\n零售油價少有變動，每個零售商旗下所有油站的燃油價格均相同。<br />\n<br />\n香港市場只提供98 辛烷值，汽油本地零售商過往聲稱只出售98 辛烷值汽油是反映顧客喜好，事實上，絕大部分車輛均能使用95 辛烷值汽油並操作順暢。(同藥房佬聲稱口罩貴因為來貨貴一樣)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/url?sa=t&amp;rct=j&amp;q=&amp;esrc=s&amp;source=web&amp;cd=2&amp;ved=2ahUKEwi23I2Y9JjoAhVHGaYKHdcQDLQQFjABegQICBAB&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.compcomm.hk%2Ftc%2Fmedia%2Fpress%2Ffiles%2FAt_a_glance_final_Chi.pdf&amp;usg=AOvVaw1cidDY5qFKaJeHMzcj8rlP\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fsa%3Dt%26rct%3Dj%26q%3D%26esrc%3Ds%26source%3Dweb%26cd%3D2%26ved%3D2ahUKEwi23I2Y9JjoAhVHGaYKHdcQDLQQFjABegQICBAB%26url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.compcomm.hk%252Ftc%252Fmedia%252Fpress%252Ffiles%252FAt_a_glance_final_Chi.pdf%26usg%3DAOvVaw1cidDY5qFKaJeHMzcj8rlP&d=B95HL5QQ1MLE%2FldfuzA7j67%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=a195dec6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/url?sa=t&amp;rct=j&amp;q=&amp;esrc=s&amp;source=web&amp;cd=2&amp;ved=2ahUKEwi23I2Y9JjoAhVHGaYKHdcQDLQQFjABegQICBAB&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.compcomm.hk%2Ftc%2Fmedia%2Fpress%2Ffiles%2FAt_a_glance_final_Chi.pdf&amp;usg=AOvVaw1cidDY5qFKaJeHMzcj8rlP</a>"},{"pid":"7c3ac6c7e6e7e4831fc522bcbdd73cea7aa53f15","tid":1924812,"uid":90304,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T02:42:29.000Z","msg":"國際油價每桶高達140多美元時，香港的柴油價格每公升約12港元，現時油價已回落至每桶60多美元，柴油價卻不跌反升，令人質疑本港油站有合謀定價之嫌。<br />\n<br />\n蔣志偉稱，非法油站存在多時，惟該類油站的衍生，很大原因來自高油價"},{"pid":"903cdc392ec4c2af4dcdb5a660f93865787010b9","tid":1924812,"uid":90304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T03:44:57.000Z","msg":"袁國勇批評政府在○三年沙士後通過興建三幢傳染病大樓，最終淪為空頭支票，直斥沒有吸取慘痛教訓，更不能想像醫院現在仍沿用十七年前的系統應對今次疫症。"},{"pid":"a39ef6d1c28e27047166e9b44c6e1dc95d563396","tid":1924812,"uid":71215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T05:11:34.000Z","msg":"dllm 垃圾政府"},{"pid":"ba1a7e412daf16c2a6741be5c8ed82d174fa1922","tid":1924812,"uid":67280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re